should work on MacOSX

to run>
make
./test <port that the thymio is connected to>

e.g.
./test /dev/cu.usbmodemfd121 

This should just send a reset signal to your robot and you
will be hearing the robot's ready signal. That's it for now!
You should also see some output on the command line like so:
juxi@home:> ./test /dev/cu.usbmodemfd121 
Connected to /dev/cu.usbmodemfd121 ... and configured!
wrote 8 bytes
received 6 bytes
juxi@home:>


That's all folks,
//Juxi <juxi@idsia.ch>